                </svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://kick.com/Tycen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Kick">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm-1 17H7V7h4v10zm8 0h-4v-5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2h-2V7h2c2.21 0 4 1.79 4 4v6z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@TycenYT" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="YouTube">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M19.615 3.184c-3.604-.246-11.631-.245-15.23 0-3.897.266-4.356 2.62-4.385 8.816.029 6.185.484 8.549 4.385 8.816 3.6.245 11.626.246 15.23 0 3.897-.266 4.356-2.62 4.385-8.816-.029-6.185-.484-8.549-4.385-8.816zm-10.615 12.816v-8l8 3.993-8 4.007z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://crealitycloud.com/user/9519489699" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Creality Cloud">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm-1 21.95c-5.513-.26-9.95-4.77-9.95-10.05 0-.789.092-1.556.264-2.292L7 16v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v2.95zm9.95-3.113c-.26-.738-1-1.267-1.838-1.337H18v-3c0-.552-.448-1-1-1h-5v-2h2c.552 0 1-.448 1-1V8h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.535C21.969 7.278 24 10.338 24 14c0 1.926-.432 3.748-1.05 5.837z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What services do you offer?</h3>
            <p>We offer a range of services including web development, content creation, crypto mining, 3D printing, and consulting. Visit our <a href="/services">Services</a> page for more information.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How can I request a quote?</h3>
            <p>You can request a quote by filling out the contact form on this page or by sending an email to <a href="mailto:info@nosytlabs.com">info@nosytlabs.com</a>.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What is your typical response time?</h3>
            <p>We typically respond to inquiries within 24-48 hours during business days.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you offer remote services?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we offer remote services for clients worldwide. We use various communication tools to ensure smooth collaboration regardless of location.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What file formats do you accept for 3D printing?</h3>
            <p>We accept STL, OBJ, and 3MF file formats for 3D printing. If you have a different format, please contact us to see if we can accommodate it.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I track my project's progress?</h3>
            <p>Once your project begins, we provide regular updates and access to project management tools where you can track progress in real-time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    padding: var(--spacing-12) 0;
  }
  
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-12);
  }
  
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-5xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  
  .dark .page-header h1 {
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }
  
  .lead {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--gray-600);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .dark .lead {
    color: var(--gray-300);
  }
  
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-16);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    }
  }
  
  .contact-form-container {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-8);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .dark .contact-form-container {
    background-color: var(--gray-800);
  }
  
  .contact-form-container h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  
  .dark .contact-form-container h2 {
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }
  
  .contact-form {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-4);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contact-form {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    
    .contact-form .form-group:nth-child(5),
    .contact-form .form-group:nth-child(6),
    .contact-form .form-group:nth-child(7),
    .contact-form .form-group:nth-child(8),
    .contact-form .form-group:nth-child(9) {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
  }
  
  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .form-group label {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
  }
  
  .form-group input,
  .form-group select,
  .form-group textarea {
    padding: var(--spacing-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-300);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-normal) var(--transition-timing-ease);
  }
  
  .dark .form-group input,
  .dark .form-group select,
  .dark .form-group textarea {
    background-color: var(--gray-700);
    border-color: var(--gray-600);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  
  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.1);
  }
  
  .dark .form-group input:focus,
  .dark .form-group select:focus,
  .dark .form-group textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--primary-light);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
  }
  
  .file-upload {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .file-upload input[type="file"] {
    padding: var(--spacing-2);
  }
  
  .file-info {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-1);
  }
  
  .dark .file-info {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }
  
  .budget-range .range-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-4);
  }
  
  .budget-range input[type="range"] {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .budget-range #budget-value {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    min-width: 80px;
  }
  
  .contact-info {
    background-color: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-8);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .dark .contact-info {
    background-color: var(--primary-light);
  }
  
  .contact-info h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--spacing-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
  }
  
  .info-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .info-content h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-1);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .info-content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-1);
  }
  
  .info-content a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-normal) var(--transition-timing-ease);
  }
  
  .info-content a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  .social-links {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-8);
  }
  
  .social-links h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .social-icons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-4);
  }
  
  .social-icons a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: white;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal) var(--transition-timing-ease);
  }
  
  .social-icons a:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  
  .faq-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-16);
  }
  
  .faq-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  
  .dark .faq-section h2 {
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }
  
  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-6);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  .faq-item {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .dark .faq-item {
    background-color: var(--gray-800);
  }
  
  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  
  .dark .faq-item h3 {
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }
  
  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }
  
  .dark .faq-item p {
    color: var(--gray-300);
  }
  
  .faq-item a {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .dark .faq-item a {
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }
</style>

